<br>
Unless the lore tags are removed <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> (do not remove this tag under penalty of law)</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, or summoned duplicate lore items are dropped instead of failing, the convenience of the bag o' focus is illusory.<br>
<br>
The main feature of the proposed spell is clearly convenience.  However, with the existing mechanics, the mage will have to drop or destroy all the focus items they are wearing first before summoning the bag.  Thus, the spell fails to fulfill its intended purpose.<br>
<br>
I have added this to the summary.<br>
<br>
